=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex8 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 301 Hz, featuring moderate attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: moderate
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: moderate
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 301.3973
  harmonic_decay_rate: -13.7553
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5008
  pitch_clarity: 12.7651
  inharmonicity: 0.0041
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -3.5207
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: UGen Example 8
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/UGen.html
// Tags: UGen, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 8 ---
{ SinOsc.ar(300, 0, 0.5) * SinOsc.kr(2).unipolar * 0.1 }.play;
